sentences: In 2016, Dazed magazine described her as "the internet's most rebellious underground rap queen".

Her second album Goldilocks X was released in September 2021.
Genesis started recording rap in 2013 as part of a project called G3NESIS.
In 2015 Genesis signed with Awful Records and released her debut mixtape World Vision.
In 2017 she signed with Downtown Records/Universal.
